{"type": "article", "id": 30604, "title": "智能取色笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-04T22:58:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804212243Q2mstz8SwPJMkdKq.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>我们曾经介绍过一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29282.html\">Spector</a> 的智能工具，在看到喜欢的颜色时只要轻轻一按就能把它储存下来。不过对于想直接进行创作的人来说，这支能够立刻使用的取色笔 Cronzy Pen 则更加实用。Cronzy 就像是一支功能更为强大的多色笔：它自带的颜色库提供多达 1600 万种颜色选择，如果你打算复制某个物品的颜色只要用尾端对其进行扫描即可。它还提供五种不同类型的笔尖以及一个用来充电的笔盒，充满后可以连续使用 7 个小时。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/cronzy-pen-over-16-million-colors-in-your-pocket-art-gadgets#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 139 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804212636RvnFTSb6CcL0jlf1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608042126346aSLMrcRYIosK2Dh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804212636pStPUis1m2c7ZLNf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804212636FopOuUwBZhj2mKyf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}